translations: 压紧的；结实的；嵌入的；（人口）稠密的
装紧；挤满（impact 的过去分词）

phrs.translation: 对于…有影响；对…造成冲击
视觉冲击，视觉震撼；视觉效果

sentences.sentence: The company's performance was impacted by the high value of the pound.
sentences.translation: 公司的业绩受到了英镑高值的冲击。

sentences.sentence: Her father's death impacted greatly on her childhood years.
sentences.translation: 父亲去世对她的童年造成巨大影响。

sentences.sentence: Though our own world was seemingly self-contained, it impacted on the white world of Piedmont in almost every direction.
sentences.translation: 虽然我们自己的世界似乎是自给自足的，但它几乎从各个方面影响着皮埃蒙特的白人世界。
